          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span><br>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FFE699\">Geo DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_8869524933299594632.png",
                "id": "talent40577",
                "key": "Sparkling Scatter",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Sparkling Scatter"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span> dan menciptakan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Jade Screen</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Jade Screen</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karakter Aktifmu menerima minimal 2 poin DMG:</span> Mengurangi 1 poin DMG yang diterima.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/2a1c2baa706dfc49f86033be36f170e9_7006649916766342820.png",
                "id": "talent59374",
                "key": "Jade Screen",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Jade Screen"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 6 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>. Jika <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Jade Screen</span> sedang berada di arena, mengakibatkan +2 poin DMG.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Jade Screen</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karakter Aktifmu menerima minimal 2 poin DMG:</span> Mengurangi 1 poin DMG yang diterima.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/55dfd3944aa4091c2684c17412739558_8050387976420762178.png",
                "id": "talent522",
                "key": "Starshatter",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Starshatter"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Bereaksi dengan Elemen jika sudah diberikan:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_8821342578643988238.png",
                "id": "talent70720",
                "key": "Geo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Geo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
